description: Lists the collected data of a Q App data collection session.

parameters.name: instanceId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the Amazon Q Business application environment instance.

parameters.name: sessionId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the Q App data collection session.

nested_items.name: sessionId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the Q App data collection session.

nested_items.name: sessionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Q App data collection session.

nested_items.name: sessionData
nested_items.description: The collected responses of a Q App session.

nested_items.name: cardId
nested_items.description: The card Id associated with the response submitted for a Q App session.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The response submitted for a Q App session.

nested_items.name: userId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of a user.

nested_items.name: submissionId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the submission.

nested_items.name: timestamp
nested_items.description: The date and time when the session data is submitted.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that indicates the next set of results to retrieve.
